{
  "stem": "294.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother and I packed little suitcases, and we went as far as the end of the city, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then my mother said, where are we going?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where will we go?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, the two women alone-- and we came back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was our biggest mistake.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Although you never knew what could have happened, because the Germans were shooting those people who were running away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were shooting them from airplanes, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They are mowing them like-- and so-- where was I?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You were-- when you met, now, Poldek, and you were in their apartment.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Poldek arranged it for my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Many doctors left there for eastern Poland, leaving their offices, their equipment, and everything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So Poldek rented it for my mother the complete office.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she practiced from the very beginning, when she came, she practiced.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we stayed for one-- for-- I think for one month or two months with this friend of ours.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then my parents-- future parents-in-law-- got their apartment back-- completely empty, but they managed to get it back.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the family moved again there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they asked us to move with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And of course, the restrictions-- everybody had to work, because if we didn't have the work permit, we couldn't stay in the city.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We couldn't received our food allotment-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was already now in 1940s.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm still talking about 1939.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it went like this till about-- 1940.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think in 1941, we went to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the-- I married my husband.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We came in November.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In February of 1940, we got engaged.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in 19-- in July of 1940, we got married.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
